question.text: An immersion heater with electrical resistance <math><mn>7</mn><mi> </mi><mi mathvariant="normal">Ω</mi></math> is immersed in 0.1 kg of water at <math><mn>20 </mn><mn>℃</mn></math> for 3 min.
